<div class="row">
    <div id="main_2" class="slab col m6 offset-m1 z-depth-1" style="margin-top: 2% !important;">
        <div class="row">
            <h3>
                Sponsorship Options
            </h3>
            <p style="text-align: justify">
                We also multiple sponsorship options. Our sponsors are offered additional benefits as stated below. The sponsors in Category I will be provided a stall in the exhibition hall and a representative from the company will be allowed to participate free. Sponsors in categories I and II will also receive the added benefit of displaying their advertisement on the ICCB website for a one year period.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <button class="btn-large modal-trigger waves-effect waves-light" data-target="sponsor" >View Categories</button>
        </div>
        <p style="text-align: justify">
            Matter for print advertisements (including quality graphics is any), banners for display at venues and on the websites as per the specified size has to be provided by the advertiser
            <br /><br />
            Please contact us at iccb2016@vit.ac.in for more details on sponsorship
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
