                </th>
                <th>
                    Advertisement (half page) in the abstract book (Page other than front and back covers)
                </th>
                <th>
                    Banner display at the inaugural /main venue till end of conference
                </th>
                <th>
                    Banner display at one of the venues till end of conference
                </th>
